Class FieldDefinitionsController

java.lang.Object
uk.pallas.systems.typr.rest.FieldDefinitionsController
@RestController("Typr Field API") @RequestMapping("api/type/v1") public class FieldDefinitionsController extends Object
This Defines an interface for retrieving Field Definitions stored within Typr.
